  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GLMapImageGroupCallback  
    GLMapManager.StateListener  
    GLMapTrackData.PointsCallback
    Callback for filling track data
    GLMapView.ResourceLoadCallback
    Called when GLMapView need to load some image
    GLMapView.ScreenCaptureCallback
    Called when GLMapView finished rendering map and text to Bitmap
    GLMapView.ScreenCaptureRawCallback
    Called when GLMapView finished rendering map and text to raw data
    GLSearchOffline.GLMapSearchCompletion  
    ProgressCallback

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GLMapBBox
    GLMapBBox is used to define some rectangular area of map
    GLMapDownloadTask
    GLMapDownloadTask downloads map and extracts it at the same time
    GLMapImage
    GLMapImage is a bridge class, to work with GLMap internal representation of image on map.
    GLMapImageGroup
    GLMapImageGroup is a bridge class, to work with GLMap internal representation of image group.
    GLMapInfo
    GLMapInfo is information object about offline map.
    GLMapLocaleSettings
    `GLMapLocaleSettings` is used to set language order to all `GLMapView` objects
    GLMapManager
    A singleton object that manages offline maps
    GLMapMarkerImage
    Class that hold information of image used by GLMapMarkerStyleCollection
    GLMapMarkerLayer
    GLMapMarkerLayer displays big number of markers with given style.
    GLMapMarkerStyleCollection
    GLMapMarkerStyleCollection class holds collection of styles, used to draw marker layer.
    GLMapMarkerStyleCollectionDataCallback
    GLMapMarkerStyleCollectionDataCallback is called for each marker or cluster to get display data
    GLMapRasterTileSource
    GLMapRasterTileSource is used to setup custom raster tile source.
    GLMapTrack
    GLMapTrack is a bridge class, to work with GLMap internal representation of track on map.
    GLMapTrackData
    Class holding data for track
    GLMapVectorCascadeStyle
    GLMapVectorCascadeStyle is used to define appearance of GLMapVectorObject.
    GLMapVectorObject
    GLMapVectorObject is a bridge class, to work with GLMap internal representation of vector object.
    GLMapVectorObjectList
    GLMapVectorObject is a bridge class, to work with GLMap internal representation of array of vector object.
    GLMapVectorStyle
    GLMapVectorStyle is used to define appearance of text inside GLMapMarkerLayer or GLMapView`.
    GLMapView
    GLMapView is a custom SurfaceView that renders and presents vector map
    GLSearchCategories
    `GLSearchCategories` class holds a set of `GLSearchCategory` that will be used to sort search results by priority.
    GLSearchCategory
    `GLSearchCategory` class holds information about category that can be displayed to user.
    GLSearchOffline
    `GLSearchOffline` class contains a set of parameters that defines search in offline maps
    ImageManager
    ImageManager used to render images from svgpb format and load images from resources.
    MapGeoPoint
    MapGeoPoint is used to store geo coordinates in WGS84 format.
    MapPoint
    MapPoint is used store coordinates in map internal format
